description: This Chainlink VRF top 10% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 34, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 170, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and 5 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50345-66152-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [170 Votes, Top 10% Score]
